10. What the proof consumes
The proof should consume an even lower-level normalized form:

inductive Region
| Global : String → Region
| Deref  : String → Nat → Region
| Local  : String → Region
| DisplayListArena : Region
| AllMemory : Region

inductive Event
| Store : Region → Event
| Call  : String → Event
| Havoc : Region → Event
| Branch : String → List Event → List Event → Event

def writesOf : Event → Set Region
| .Store r => {r}
| .Havoc r => {r}
| .Call f  => summaryWrites f
| .Branch _ t e => writesOfList t ∪ writesOfList e
Then the generic theorem is:

theorem preserved_if_not_written :
  r ∉ writesOfProgram p →
  readRegion r (exec p mem) = readRegion r mem
That theorem is independent of SM64. It is the reusable core.

